Package: chap.r.sdk
Title: Chap SDK for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Knut", "Rand", , "knutdrand@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides convenience functionality for developing chap-compatible
    models and integrating existing models with chap. Includes utilities for
    creating command line interfaces, model validation, spatio-temporal data
    transformations, and configuration schema management.
